                //                 "content": "<p class="\"art_p\""> </p><p class="\"art_p\""><img src="\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/400/w1000h1000/20180502/QvQg-fzyqqip9726508.jpg\"" img-size="\"1000,1000\"" class="mCS_img_loaded"></p><p class="\"art_p\"">勇士今日迎来库里复出，在他的率领下，勇士主场再胜鹈鹕，一起来看看Reddit球迷们怎么评价这场比赛！</p><p class="\"art_p\"">——————————————</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]LakersItDontMata 116 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">I hate how likeable Curry is</p><p class="\"art_p\"">库里这么讨人爱真是好讨厌啊嘤嘤嘤</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]Warriorscaramelfrap 263 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">came off the bench AND got 28 points with a +29, just Curry things</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Curry for 6th man of the year</p><p class="\"art_p\"">替补出场、拿了28分、正负值+29，这就是库里的常规操作。</p><p class="\"art_p\"">库里是年度最佳第六人！</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]KnicksDeeliciousness 16 points 2 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">At one point a graphic said something like: Warriors with Curry: +24 Warriors without: -23</p><p class="\"art_p\"">比赛中一度有过一个字幕：库里在场勇士赢24分，不在场勇士输23分。</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]WarriorsHelloIAmANarwhal 253 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Is there any doubt he is the best pg in the league?</p><p class="\"art_p\"">他是联盟最佳控卫还有疑问吗？</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]Warriorschugginjuice 47 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">There's been doubt?</p><p class="\"art_p\"">有过疑问吗？</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]Rockets Bandwagonlivefreeordont 232 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Not, for the last 4 years lmao where you been</p><p class="\"art_p\"">早没了兄弟，过去四年他都是，你这段时间是去哪了？</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]WarriorsBoredomHeights 330 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Prisons. I’ve been in a lot of prisons.</p><p class="\"art_p\"">去坐牢了，我坐了好多牢...</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]LakersPalifaith 84 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">It's gonna be Warriors vs. Cavs again isn't it?</p><p class="\"art_p\"">是要再来一次勇士vs骑士，对吧？</p><p class="\"art_p\"">————————————</p><p class="\"art_p\""><img src="\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/133/w598h335/20180502/SbWj-fzyqqip9726531.jpg\"" img-size="\"598,335\"" class="mCS_img_loaded"></p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–][GSW] Andre Iguodalapwnrmasta_01 915 points 3 hours ago*</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Klay shot 4/20 tonight</p><p class="\"art_p\"">克莱今天20投16铁啊</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]ahabooo 46 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Klay Thompson is UNDEFEATED when he went 4-20 in the playoff</p><p class="\"art_p\"">当克莱在季后赛里20中4的情况下，他的球队保持全胜。</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]WarriorsVampireBatman 253 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Klay went full Trailblazer tonight.</p><p class="\"art_p\"">克莱进入了开拓者模式</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–][GSW] Draymond Greennotabear629 62 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Or full Kyle Lowry depending on how you look at it</p><p class="\"art_p\"">或者洛瑞模式吧，看你怎么说了。</p><p class="\"art_p\"">————————————</p><p class="\"art_p\""><img src="\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/686/w743h743/20180502/_m0G-fzyqqip9726560.jpg\"" img-size="\"743,743\"" class="mCS_img_loaded"></p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]WarriorsCtG526 489 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Wow, that guy on our bench really played well tonight.</p><p class="\"art_p\"">哇塞！我勇这个替补今天打得真棒棒诶！</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]WarriorsBoredomHeights 3 points 3 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Maybe he'll get a deal like Quinn Cook got if he has a few more games like this.</p><p class="\"art_p\"">如果他再打出几场这样的表现，他大概就能拿到奎因-库克那样的合同了！</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]Warriorsunequivocalotter 18 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">BENCH MOB</p><p class="\"art_p\"">板凳上的萌面匪徒啊！</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]76ersEarthWindandFlyers 403 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">This Steph Curry guy is pretty good. Maybe some day he'll be a starter.</p><p class="\"art_p\"">这个叫斯呆芬-咖喱的家伙挺不错的，也许他未来能成为一个先发球员。</p><p class="\"art_p\"">[–]TimberwolvesMonsterDevourer 16 points 4 hours ago</p><p class="\"art_p\"">Idk I don't really see him taking A